FBIS4-21915 "jptot015__l94080" JPRS-TOT-94-015-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 6 April 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA ISRAEL Hamas Carbomb in 'Afula Kills Eight, Wounds 50 Hamas Carbomb in 'Afula Kills Eight, Wounds 50 Hamas Takes Credit, Names `Terrorist' TA0604151094 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1400 GMT 6 Apr 94 TA0604151094 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Hebrew BFN [Text] Hamas [Islamic Resistance Movement] has assumed responsibility for the 'Afula attack, claiming that its men perpetrated the attack. In a leaflet distributed in Janin, Hamas said that the name of the suicide terrorist is Ra'id Zakarnah, 19, of Qabatiyah. Our correspondent Moti Amir reports that a short while ago, the security forces arrived in Qabatiyah, and took Zakarnah's father to the Ha'emeq Hospital to identify the body.
